                This shift has occurred with the full support of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Congress</ENAMEX>, both major political
                <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">parties</ENAMEX>, the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">media</ENAMEX>, and the <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">American</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">people</ENAMEX>.
