                terrorism. <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Between fiscal year 2001</TIMEX>, the last budget adopted before <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">9/11</TIMEX>, and the
                present <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">fiscal year 2004</TIMEX>, total federal spending on defense (including expenditures
