                Recommendation: We endorse the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">American National Standards</ENAMEX>
                    <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Institute's</ENAMEX> recommended standard for private preparedness. We were encouraged by
                    <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Secretary</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Tom Ridge</ENAMEX>'s praise of the standard, and urge the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Department of</ENAMEX>
                    <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Homeland Security</ENAMEX> to promote its adoption. We also encourage the insurance and
                    credit-rating <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">industries</ENAMEX> to look closely at a <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">company</ENAMEX>'s compliance with the ANSI
