                    <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">company</ENAMEX> to its <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">employees</ENAMEX> and the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">public</ENAMEX> for legal purposes. Private-sector
